# Reimu wearing Imadakedabuchitabemi's outfit

It seems Reimu prefers a Big Mac over a Double Cheeseburger.

> Reimu's badge here is the "**Haku**" part of her "Hakurei" surname, just like how it is "**Ima**" in "[**Imadakedabuchitabemi**](https://x.com/McDonaldsJapan/status/1848552354464838013)"
